# Final Structure

This is a **lexicographic linear programming model**:

1. Satisfy blending constraints (hard).
2. Maximize profit.
3. Among optimal-profit solutions, maximize satisfaction of  
   \(Q_R \ge 2000\) (or minimize shortfall if infeasible).

