\]

#### 2. Each position occupied by exactly one job
\[
\sum_{j \in J} x_{jk} = 1 \qquad \forall k \in K
\]

#### 3. Completion times on machine A

For \( k = 1 \):
\[
C^A_1 \ge \sum_{j \in J} A_j x_{j1}
\]

For \( k = 2,\dots,6 \):
\[
C^A_k \ge C^A_{k-1} + \sum_{j \in J} A_j x_{jk}
