#### Other parameters

- Monthly production capacity:
\[
\sum_{i} x_{it} \le 120000
\]

- Volume per unit:
\[
v_1 = 0.2, \quad v_2 = 0.4
\]

- Internal warehouse capacity:
\[
15000 \text{ m}^3
\]

- Internal storage cost: 1 yuan/m³/month  
- External storage cost: 1.5 yuan/m³/month  

