## Coverage Constraints

For each month \( t = 1,2,3,4 \):

\[
\sum_{i=1}^{t}
\sum_{\substack{d \ge t-i+1 \\ i+d-1 \le 4}}
x_{i,d}
\;\ge\;
D_t
\qquad
t=1,2,3,4
\]

This ensures that all contracts active in month \( t \) cover the required warehouse area.

---

## Nonnegativity

\[
x_{i,d} \ge 0
\quad
\text{for all valid } (i,d)
\]

