x_{1B}+x_{2B}+x_{3B} &= 20 \\
x_{1C}+x_{2C}+x_{3C} &= 20
\end{aligned}
\]

---

### Minimum Shipment Requirements

\[
\begin{aligned}
x_{2A}+x_{2B}+x_{2C} &\ge 38 \\
x_{3A}+x_{3B}+x_{3C} &\ge 27
\end{aligned}
\]

---

### Nonnegativity

\[
x_{ij} \ge 0
\]

