5.23 A university computer lab hires 4 undergraduate students (IDs 1, 2, 3, 4) and 2 graduate students (IDs 5, 6) for duty and consultation shifts. The maximum duty time each person can be scheduled for from Monday to Friday and their hourly wage are shown in Table 5-9.  

