### Decision Variables
\[
z_{i,a,b} =
\begin{cases}
1 & \text{if department } i \text{ receives } (a,b) \\
0 & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
\]
\[
z_{i,a,b} \in \{0,1\}
\]

### Objective Function
\[
\max \sum_{i \in I} \sum_{a \in X} \sum_{b \in Y} R_i(a,b)\, z_{i,a,b}
\]

### Constraints

#### 1. Each department receives exactly one allocation:
\[
\sum_{a \in X} \sum_{b \in Y} z_{i,a,b} = 1 \qquad \forall i \in I
\]

#### 2. Total use of resource 1:
\[
\sum_{i \in I} \sum_{a \in X} \sum_{b \in Y} a\, z_{i,a,b} = \bar X
\]

#### 3. Total use of resource 2:
\[
\sum_{i \in I} \sum_{a \in X} \sum_{b \in Y} b\, z_{i,a,b} = \bar Y
\]

#### 4. Binary restrictions:
\[
z_{i,a,b} \in \{0,1\} \qquad \forall i \in I,\; a \in X,\; b \in Y
\]

