【数学模型】:
 **Mathematical Model (Mixed-Integer Linear Programming Formulation)**  

---

### Sets and Index
\[
t = 1,2,3,4,5,6 \quad \text{(months)}
\]

---

### Parameters

(All quantities measured in **hundreds of units**)

\[
\begin{aligned}
&d_t = \text{demand in month } t \\
& (d_1,d_2,d_3,d_4,d_5,d_6) = (1,2,5,3,2,1) \\
\\
&\text{Production capacity: } P^{\max} = 4 \\
&\text{Storage capacity: } I^{\max} = 3 \\
\\
&c_p = 10000 \quad \text{(production cost per 100 units)} \\
&c_h = 1000 \quad \text{(inventory holding cost per 100 units per month)} \\
&F = 4000 \quad \text{(fixed production cost per month if production occurs)}
\end{aligned}
\]

