### Decision Variables

\[
\begin{aligned}
&x_t \ge 0 \quad \text{production quantity in month } t \text{ (hundreds)} \\
&I_t \ge 0 \quad \text{inventory at end of month } t \text{ (hundreds)} \\
&y_t \in \{0,1\} \quad \text{1 if production occurs in month } t,\;0\text{ otherwise}
\end{aligned}
\]

---

### Objective Function

Minimize total cost:

\[
\min Z =
\sum_{t=1}^{6} \left( c_p x_t + c_h I_t + F y_t \right)
\]

