  <html><body><table><tr><td>Patrol Units \ Warehouse </td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>18</td><td>38</td><td>14</td><td>34</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>16</td><td>36</td><td>12</td><td>31</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>12</td><td>30</td><td>11</td><td>25</td></tr></table></body></html>


-------------
【数学模型】:
 ### Decision Variables

Let  

\[
x_{ij} =
\begin{cases}
1, & \text{if } j \text{ patrol units are assigned to warehouse } i \\
0, & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
\]

where:

- \( i = 1,2,3,4 \) (warehouses)  
- \( j \in \{2,3,4\} \) (number of patrol units assigned)

---

### Parameters (Expected Accidents)

Let \( c_{ij} \) denote the expected annual accidents if warehouse \( i \) is assigned \( j \) patrol units.

\[
\begin{aligned}
&c_{1,2}=18,\; c_{1,3}=16,\; c_{1,4}=12 \\
&c_{2,2}=38,\; c_{2,3}=36,\; c_{2,4}=30 \\
&c_{3,2}=14,\; c_{3,3}=12,\; c_{3,4}=11 \\
&c_{4,2}=34,\; c_{4,3}=31,\; c_{4,4}=25
\end{aligned}
\]

Total patrol units available: 12.

---

### Objective Function

Minimize total expected accidents:

\[
\min Z =
\sum_{i=1}^{4} \sum_{j=2}^{4} c_{ij} x_{ij}
\]

Expanded form:

\[
\begin{aligned}
\min Z =\;&
18x_{1,2}+16x_{1,3}+12x_{1,4} \\
&+38x_{2,2}+36x_{2,3}+30x_{2,4} \\
&+14x_{3,2}+12x_{3,3}+11x_{3,4} \\
&+34x_{4,2}+31x_{4,3}+25x_{4,4}
\end{aligned}
\]

---

### Constraints

#### 1. Each warehouse must receive exactly one allocation level

\[
\sum_{j=2}^{4} x_{ij} = 1, \quad i=1,2,3,4
\]

---

#### 2. Total patrol units used must equal 12

\[
\sum_{i=1}^{4} \sum_{j=2}^{4} j \, x_{ij} = 12
\]

Expanded:

\[
\begin{aligned}
&2x_{1,2}+3x_{1,3}+4x_{1,4} \\
+&2x_{2,2}+3x_{2,3}+4x_{2,4} \\
+&2x_{3,2}+3x_{3,3}+4x_{3,4} \\
+&2x_{4,2}+3x_{4,3}+4x_{4,4}
= 12
\end{aligned}
\]

---

#### 3. Binary constraints

\[
x_{ij} \in \{0,1\}, \quad i=1,2,3,4;\; j=2,3,4
\]

---

### Final Model

\[
\boxed{
\begin{aligned}
\min \quad & \sum_{i=1}^{4} \sum_{j=2}^{4} c_{ij} x_{ij} \\
\text{s.t.} \quad
& \sum_{j=2}^{4} x_{ij} = 1, && i=1,\dots,4 \\
& \sum_{i=1}^{4} \sum_{j=2}^{4} j\, x_{ij} = 12 \\
& x_{ij} \in \{0,1\}
\end{aligned}
}
\]
