\[
\sum_{\substack{i<j \\ i,j \in S}} x_{ij} \le |S| - 1
\qquad \forall S \subset V,\; 2 \le |S| \le 8
\]

### Binary Constraints

\[
x_{ij} \in \{0,1\}
\qquad \forall (i,j)\in E
\]

