For a nurse starting on day \( d \):

- Works Shift 1 on day \( d \)
- Works Shift 2 on day \( d+1 \)
- Works Shift 3 on day \( d+2 \)
- Works Shift 4 on day \( d+3 \)
- Works Shift 5 on day \( d+4 \)

(indices modulo 7)

